<h3>Your Locale</h3>
<p>The system supports multiple currency symbols, including the Euro.&nbsp; Select which part of the world you are from and the system will change the currency symbol to whatever symbol you use in your part of the world.&nbsp; If you use the Euro, be sure to select Yes for using the Euro symbol or the system will use the standard currency symbol for the region you select (for instance, it will use&nbsp;the English Pound sign unless you tell the system to use the Euro).</p>




